snippet.title: 10 Pin: Champions Alley - PlayStation 2 Gameplay
snippet.description:
Roll into action with 10 Pin: Champions Alley, the easy to play bowling game that lets you play alone or with up to seven friends.

Developed by Atomic Planet Entertainment Limited
Published by OG International Entertainment (Liquid Games)
